# Schema configuration

## Basics
{: .col-2}

### Minimal configuration

```elixir
defmodule Pet do
  use Ecto.Schema

  @derive {
    Flop.Schema,
    filterable: [:name, :species],
    sortable: [:name, :age]
  }

  schema "pets" do
    field :name, :string
    field :age, :integer
    field :species, :string
  end
end
```

### Options

#### Limit

```elixir
@derive {
  Flop.Schema,
  filterable: [:name, :species],
  sortable: [:name, :age],
  max_limit: 100,
  default_limit: 50
}
```

#### Order

```elixir
@derive {
  Flop.Schema,
  filterable: [:name, :species],
  sortable: [:name, :age],
  default_order: %{
    order_by: [:name, :age],
    order_directions: [:asc, :desc]
  }
}
```

#### Pagination types

```elixir
@derive {
  Flop.Schema,
  filterable: [:name, :species],
  sortable: [:name, :age],
  pagination_types: [:first, :last],
  default_pagination_type: :first
}
```

## Alias fields
{: .col-2}

### Schema

```elixir
defmodule Owner do
  use Ecto.Schema

  @derive {
    Flop.Schema,
    filterable: [:name],
    sortable: [:name, :pet_count],
    adapter_opts: [
      alias_fields: [:pet_count]
    ]
  }

  schema "owners" do
    field :name, :string
    has_many :pets, Pet
  end
end
```

### Query

```elixir
params = %{order_by: [:pet_count]}

Owner
|> join(:left, [o], p in assoc(o, :pets), as: :pets)
|> group_by([o], o.id)
|> select(
  [o, pets: p],
  {o.id, p.id |> count() |> selected_as(:pet_count)}
)
|> Flop.validate_and_run(params, for: Owner)
```

## Compound fields
{: .col-2}

### Schema

```elixir
defmodule User do
  use Ecto.Schema

  @derive {
    Flop.Schema,
    filterable: [:full_name],
    sortable: [:full_name],
    adapter_opts: [
      compound_fields: [
        full_name: [:family_name, :given_name]
      ]
    ]
  }

  schema "users" do
    field :family_name, :string
    field :given_name, :string
  end
end
```

### Query

```elixir
params = %{
  filters: [
    %{field: :full_name, op: :ilike_and, value: "pea"}
  ]
}

Flop.validate_and_run(User, params, for: Owner)
```

